he didn't love me.

22
00:01:32,470 --> 00:01:35,304
Are you sure this was meant for me?

23
00:01:35,304 --> 00:01:37,937
If you want to know how
he really feels about you,

24
00:01:37,937 --> 00:01:39,670
let's just get married.

25
