Plus, it's not a real marriage anyway.

30
00:01:57,404 --> 00:01:59,904
This time, the bait is Seo Yun Jae.

31
00:02:00,770 --> 00:02:02,904
If you don't want to lose him again,
take the bait.

32
00:02:26,004 --> 00:02:27,404
Gyeong Jun!

33
00:02:30,770 --> 00:02:32,637
No way!

34
00:02:32,637 --> 00:02:33,570
