We can't let it happen.

538
00:36:38,104 --> 00:36:41,237
You don't want your mom
remarrying either, do you?

539
00:36:41,937 --> 00:36:45,770
I'll tell my dad I'm sick
and keep him at home,

540
00:36:45,770 --> 00:36:48,371
so you also make sure your
mother doesn't come over.

541
00:36:48,804 --> 00:36:50,804
Okay?

542
00:36:51,304 --> 00:36:53,371
You promise, right?

543
00:37:01,404 --> 00:37:03,937
That night,

544
00:37:06,237 --> 00:37:10,937
Gyeong Jun's mother

545
00:37:10,937 --> 00:37:14,804
was shot

546
00:37:14,804 --> 00:37:16,870
and killed.

547
00:37:20,870 --> 00:37:24,704
She wouldn't have died if
she had come to see my dad.

548
00:37:26,404 --> 00:37:29,338
It was all my fault.

549
00:37:52,271 --> 00:37:54,338
Gyeong Jun.

550
00:38:08,804 --> 00:38:10,737
Gyeong Jun,

551
00:38:11,770 --> 00:38:14,037
I have to go somewhere tonight.

552
00:38:14,037 --> 00:38:16,904
Don't go.

553
00:38:17,603 --> 00:38:19,737
If you go,

554
00:38:19,737 --> 00:38:22,503
I won't ever see you again.

555
00:38:24,637 --> 00:38:25,970
Okay.

556
00:38:25,970 --> 00:38:28,537
I'll stay with you then.

557
00:38:32,271 --> 00:38:33,904
Hey, you.

558
00:38:53,937 --> 00:38:57,637
I didn't want anyone else in my mom's life.

559
00:38:59,438 --> 00:39:03,237
I was a brat,

560
00:39:04,438 --> 00:39:07,470
which is why I lost my mom forever.

561
00:39:18,338 --> 00:39:20,603
It wasn't your fault.

562
00:39:21,470 --> 00:39:23,937
You were

563
