just upset, like Chung Sik.

564
00:39:29,137 --> 00:39:31,438
What happened wasn't your fault.

565
00:39:41,970 --> 00:39:45,371
I asked you over for lunch to thank you

566
00:39:45,371 --> 00:39:48,371
for helping us find Chung Sik.

567
00:39:48,371 --> 00:39:52,438
I said I was coming here, and Ms. Lee
said she wanted to come with me.

568
00:39:53,171 --> 00:39:55,304
I said I wanted to come for the dumplings,

569
00:39:55,304 --> 00:39:59,237
and Vice Principal Kim said
she wanted to see you, sir.

570
00:39:59,237 --> 00:40:03,304
It's been a long time, Min Gyu.

571
00:40:03,304 --> 00:40:04,837
Yes.

572
00:40:04,837 --> 00:40:08,237
It sure has been a long time, Yeong Ok.

573
00:40:08,237 --> 00:40:09,570
You were a dear...

574
00:40:11,004 --> 00:40:12,804
I, mean, a junior colleague.

575
00:40:12,804 --> 00:40:15,503
We worked at the same school
for a very long time, didn't we?

576
00:40:15,503 --> 00:40:16,404
Yes.

577
00:40:16,404 --> 00:40:17,937
We also taught the same grade twice.

578
00:40:17,937 --> 00:40:19,404
Yes.

579
00:40:19,404 --> 00:40:22,770
She was my homeroom teacher
in my senior year.

580
00:40:22,770 --> 00:40:24,371
Oh...

581
00:40:24,371 --> 00:40:27,438
It's been so long, Ms. Kim.

582
00:40:30,404 --> 00:40:35,537
You've aged a lot, Jeong Hye.

583
00:40:35,537 --> 00:40:40,237
Age enhances one's intellect

584
00:40:40,237 --> 00:40:42,037
but diminishes one's beauty, right?

585
00:40:42,037 --> 00:40:47,937
You still have a way of getting
under people's skin, don't you?

586
00:40:49,404 --> 00:40:52,704
And you're still an airhead.

587
00:40:55,870 --> 00:40:57,704
Yeong Ok was very bright.

588
00:40:57,704 --> 00:40:59,271
Welcome.

589
00:41:02,371 --> 00:41:03,837
What would you like?

590
00:41:04,937 --> 00:41:06,137
Pork dumplings.

591
00:41:06,137 --> 00:41:07,670
Pork dumplings?

592
00:41:07,670 --> 00:41:09,237
Pork dumplings.

593
00:41:10,037 --> 00:41:12,137
